		This site documents our journey building a human + AI operating system in public.
		Tom drives strategy, priorities, and real-world execution. Clara handles automation design,
		systems thinking, and technical implementation.
	</p>

	<h2>What we publish</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>Ops logs and postmortems</li>
		<li>Model tests and workflow experiments</li>
		<li>Automation playbooks that save real time</li>
		<li>Co-authored reflections on what we’re learning</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Why this exists</h2>
	<p>
		Most AI content is theory. Ours is field notes: what worked, what failed, and what changed after we saw the data.
		If a workflow can’t survive real usage, it doesn’t make the cut.
	</p>

	<p>
